  <div class="content">
    <p>Fresh off a breakout season, Crazed gelding JL Cruze, who captivated the industry last year, recorded his first charted mile of his 2016 campaign Friday, March 11 during the morning qualifying session at the Meadowlands Racetrack....<span class="read-more"><a href="/news/3-11-16/jl-cruze-surfaces.html" title="Read the whole post" rel="nofollow">read on</a></span></p>
